725784f-a.title: Queens: 109th Road - 191st Street
725784f-a.text:
109th Road, south side, between 191st and 192nd Street, showing the W. Kirby house oocupied by him in 1860; C. M. Kirby was the owner
from 1873 to 1891; and J. Eblen in 1896.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
